title: Euro Fishng Lilies-CODEX
description:
Lilies is a 10 acre venue that is as beautiful as its residents and
      is named after the abundance of lilies on the surface of  the lake.
      This venue is known for its big fish and provides a  challenge with
      lots of weed present and the stock of fish being low. However, with
      every fish  being of  specimen size  with Carp  up to  50  lbs  and
      Catfish to 100lbs the rewards are definitely there.

      For more info go to : http://store.steampowered.com/app/321478/
